thread.title: Paul Bucknall
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Paul Bucknall

author: Paul Bucknall
title: Paul Bucknall
text: The Quote: for 2 bulky parcels weighing a total of 26kg was one third that of Auspost and included insurance. They were picked up in Newcastle at 1:30pm on 14/3/17 and was ready for the buyer to pick up at 12pm on 16/3/17 in Melbourne. Arrived in perfect order and the tracking and follow up call from the courier were spot on. Very highly recommended.
